      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Algorithm : - \n\n1 - Save head in temp \n\n2 - loop through temp and temp.next\n    \n3 - calculate the GDC of both\n\n4 - Now convert this gdc to linked node because right now it is a int\n\n5 - now insert this GDC node in between these two values\n\n6 - when done  move or increament the temp to calulate gdc for all \n\n\n\n            ",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Algorithm : - \n\n1 - Save head in temp \n\n2 - loop through temp and temp.next\n    \n3 - calculate the GDC of both\n\n4 - Now convert this gdc to linked node because right now it is a int\n\n5 - now insert this GDC node in between these two values\n\n6 - when done  move or increament the temp to calulate gdc for all \n\n\n\n            ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
